node.text: As seen at Monaco Yacht Club. Origin fuoco combines the finest Carrara marble with a customisable fire pit with remote control to create a powerful visual and tactile spectacle for the senses. Suitable for interior and exterior use. After a successful launch of Origin fuoco Studio Celiberti are delighted to launch Origin elettrica, a new cooking and dining experience in collaboration with Sub-Zero & Wolf. The Origin collection is bespoke and therefore can be customised to meet your requirements.

node.text:
Describe this waterfront house in one word!
Set amongst the dramatic landscape of Barbados’ East Coast, Zazen is a totally unique, ultra-modern escape like no other. Cutting-edge architecture is boldly brought to life in polished concrete and agate amidst a tropical breeze and the sound of waves crashing in the distance.
On making your grand entrance, discover the very finest luxury interiors set in an awe-inspiring 6,000 sq. ft. of pure luxury. Open-plan living spills out over the infinity pool, across the white sand and above and beyond the magnificent Atlantic Ocean – and the finest surf the island has to offer. For anything else, our bespoke concierge service will ensure every other detail is just as perfect.
Check @diamantemglobalportfolio for more details.
#diamantemglobalportfolio #arch_impressive

node.title: ZAZEN from @diamantemglobalportfolio WHERE ZEN AND LUXURY COME TOGETHER!

For a finish,a plant based mixture of oils and waxes.
